# Toolkit Crates

The following lists the set of crates currently included in this repository (and Rust workspace), they are not yet 
complete and will probably be joined by others over time.


[![core](https://img.shields.io/badge/RDFtk-core-BD1B89?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](./rdftk_core) This crate provides the core RDF data model; concrete implementations for `Statement`s and `Literal`s, along with a `Resource` type that provides a builder-like experience for models.

[![io](https://img.shields.io/badge/RDFtk-io-BD1B89?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](./rdftk_io) This crate provides traits for reading and writing `Statement`s and `Graph`s as well as implementations of these for common representations.

[![iri](https://img.shields.io/badge/RDFtk-iri-BD1B89?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](./rdftk_iri) This crate provides an implementation of the `IRI` and `URI` specifications.

[![names](https://img.shields.io/badge/RDFtk-names-BD1B89?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](./rdftk_names) This crate provides a set of modules that contain the `IRI`s and `QName` strings for commonly used vocabularies. It also provides macro support for defining new namespaces in the same style as this library.

[![ontology](https://img.shields.io/badge/RDFtk-ontology-BD1B89?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](./rdftk_ontology) This crate provides a data model for creating ontologies using [RDF Schema](https://www.w3.org/TR/rdf-schema/) and [OWL 2 Web Ontology Language (OWL)](https://www.w3.org/TR/owl2-overview/).

[![query](https://img.shields.io/badge/RDFtk-query-BD1B89?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](./rdftk_query) This crate provides a placeholder for a query APIs and the [*SPARQL Query Language for RDF*](https://www.w3.org/TR/rdf-sparql-query/) support.

[![skos](https://img.shields.io/badge/RDFtk-skos-BD1B89?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](./rdftk_skos) A data model with RDF support for the Simple Knowledge Organization System (SKOS) vocabulary.
